description: BentoML is an open-source platform that simplifies the deployment of machine learning models. It supports frameworks like TensorFlow, PyTorch, and Scikit-learn, allowing models to be packaged with dependencies and served as APIs. BentoML ensures scalability, versioning, and easy integration with CI/CD pipelines for production use.
